Come on! Let’s go back to work!

711
00:36:23,330 --> 00:36:23,850
Mr. Ma,

712
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:26,090
you are…

713
00:36:27,010 --> 00:36:28,330
Hold back your sympathy.

714
00:36:28,490 --> 00:36:29,570
