Mr. Lin, you wanna see me?

733
00:37:12,570 --> 00:37:13,050
Jiang Jun.

734
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:13,690
Here.

735
00:37:13,930 --> 00:37:15,410
Come here. Take a seat.

736
00:37:19,370 --> 00:37:21,330
How do you like my new office?

737
